         <abstract>
            <p>The integral $$I^{\alpha,\beta}_\nu(x) = \int^\infty_0 t^{2\alpha-1}(1 + t^2)^{1-\alpha-\beta} J_\nu(x\sqrt{1 + t^2)} dt$$ is expressed in terms of Bessel and related functions for various values of the parameters by summing the hypergeometric series representation given by Schmidt.</p>
